Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.07,0:00:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于安静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里到底会建成什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是荞麦面店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们住在附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开张之后请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若、叶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个袋子上的写的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是大泉公园站水果店前的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 这是枇杷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 请吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是邻居的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必光临尝尝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是邻居 其实就在隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工地很吵呢 对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后还请多多关照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:45.45,标题2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,450)}{\pos(360,370)}{\fs50}{\3c&H0080FF&}会长大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是若叶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在小5的时候就已经去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我指的是 如果她还在世的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的若叶 还是小五那时的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想过高中生的若叶会是怎样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到刚才为止呢 对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枇杷的核太大了吧?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜欢吃荞麦面的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像会开荞麦面店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光家旁边不是正进行工程吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 之前的住客搬走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 会开成荞麦面店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吃荞麦面的小光一定很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近都没有像样点的荞麦面店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 给我钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过今天要去买衣服的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对啊对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也选些女性化的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你除了校服外 你连一条裙子都没有吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 青叶要去那里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友去购物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是女性朋友 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 难得不用练习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想约她去看电影的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 有夏日祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 约青叶一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个的话 棒球部练习结束后也能赶得上呢 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青叶!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张传单是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 附近好像会有荞麦面店会开张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~ 好吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以准备晚饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄平回来吃晚饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说今天会回家睡 所以不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如把窗帘拉上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很吵的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工地很吵吧 对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 也不是很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁终于安静下来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日祭的彩排好像开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 是祭典的彩排啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真是令人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天的傍晚 我就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天要去夏日祭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光 光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 若叶… 奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在发什么呆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了野营回来就去夏日祭的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 若叶?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 若叶!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是荞麦面店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 青叶 明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹钟不响了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚买回来不久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跌坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没跌过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有好多凹痕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为有时候会使用其他的东西来关掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如身边的金属球棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔啊 爸爸不会出钱吧?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的零花钱买吗?我很穷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧!我替你修好它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:09:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道我很灵巧的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情再简单不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻而易举!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水辉连晚饭也不吃 在干什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭菜都凉了 去叫他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是~~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的!什么轻而易举了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好了修好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看!连凹陷的地方也修好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点去吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵巧…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东那家伙居然偷懒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道那家伙在家也会训练的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 今天要去夏日祭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫上能穿着浴衣角色的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这种空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我家酒铺要摆刨冰店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要来帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去 那中西呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我PASS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和今日子有约吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 说是要请我吃炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪你去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了！随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和树多村一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有约了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛的结果好好地报告给小若听哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会去的吧 夏日祭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若叶会生气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就加油到明年不会被骂的程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2回上半 龙旺早早就迎来了得分机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2出局 2垒有人 打者是4棒三岛敬太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打出去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光今年也打算一个人去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…他会和小若一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经6年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光刚才出门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪啊 现在其实应该是在甲子园了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的那个梦应该不是高1时的梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么… 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不穿浴衣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛要穿啊 麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为修好闹钟的回礼我才陪你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要抱怨的话就不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没、没 完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一叶姐 小若已经吃过这个点心了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有 你刚才吃过自己的份了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日祭不是在那边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前有要去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小若 吃过了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里啊 青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫墓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫墓？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊 若叶的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去厕所 马上就回来 小的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…小的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等久等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去世的人也会长大吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看 看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 很忙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 赤石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比捕手更适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到千田了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃多少啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便啦 反正是夏日祭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是祭典 你也是吃这么多的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！和这家伙突然遇到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛 别不好意思了 气氛不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正在减肥中 别让他吃太多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 轮到你说吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你们！我这里很忙的 不买的话快点走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会买的啦 汽水2瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要草莓刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还要吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 汽水2瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 赤石你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 中西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵也会长大的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了 爸爸 妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是说在入口等我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太开心了所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是我们搬迁过去的邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 不是有吗 体育用品店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 有的有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的儿子 叫做…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 我还没问过名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树多村 光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是泷川 多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泷川先生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他们的女儿 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 现在才说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:18:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话 一起逛逛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 难得遇上 一起吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不… 我就在此 先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你为我带路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小哥 你在这里发呆会很危险的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.49,0:19:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看！小若的浴衣哦 吓了你一跳吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晃眼看去很像若叶的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是姐妹 相似是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因为长得像就心动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不… 我只是开个小玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没看到你的姐妹吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 不是说那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵也会长大的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青叶！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太吵了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对着前辈你那是啥口气啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 你真的很烦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生这词不是这样用的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 回去的时候你要好好的送回去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还要问吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你死去的姐姐就这么的相似吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记忆里的姐姐就保持在小5时的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了同样的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.04,0:22:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从树多村听说了 你们是3姐妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是4姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:22:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 CROSSXGAME 第32话 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泷川茜 圣泉女子学园2年生 6月25日生 血型A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:19.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不管何时 照亮着我的光芒一直都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:49.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你与我之间 隔着那看不到的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:58.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}流逝着也没办法 任性的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:10.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}即使这样能在一起的话 有着相同的温度的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:21.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}比起口头的话语 相互接触的话会更加了解的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:30.54,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}就算是那不会燃起的恋情 这时也认为会很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:37.41,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}夏日的闪电 震撼夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:45.61,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}苍白地照亮了胆小的你 Summer rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:52.62,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}呆然而立的两人 无聊的藏在伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:01:00.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}拨开错综复杂的人群 向着拥挤的人群奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:07.92,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}手和手紧紧相握在塑料把手上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:15.37,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}僵硬的手指在每次电闪雷鸣时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:22.77,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}现在 与你一同在雨中 将那个夏天冲走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:30.31,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我心中积满着沙砾般的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:37.78,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}现在 与你一同在雨中 心中想起了谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:45.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}两人伴随着伞的 Summer rain
